{"tid":251192,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[有文字直播]2016-17 LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽升班附四強首回合","createTime":"2017-05-20T16:49:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-21T11:24:38.000Z","uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"65df3b970d8563ba2d63e1700c19092512a491fb","tid":251192,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:49:42.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">LIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽升班附加賽四強首回合</div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">2017-5-21 2pm-7pm *括號內數字為聯賽最終排名</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/JVaMPfA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FJVaMPfA.png&h=09294568&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/lXgAk8o.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FlXgAk8o.png&h=e531dede&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(9)何雁詩vs周慧敏(6)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/hCSaStY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FhCSaStY.png&h=3ec0a235&s={SIZE}\" />  <img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/zyUEMKw.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FzyUEMKw.png&h=79514674&s={SIZE}\" /></div><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">(8)駱文捷vs游蕙禎(7)</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">升班附加賽四強賽時為五小時，會員可於指定時段於以回覆投票方式揀選心水賽事女神。<br />\n在<span style=\"color: red;\">指定時段外</span>的回覆投票<span style=\"color: red;\">將不作計算</span>在內，請會員密切留意比賽時間。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">會員需清晰指出賽事投選女神，亦可選擇性投票予心水賽事。如會員同時投予兩位參賽者，將視為會員選擇和局，不投票增加該場比賽任何參賽者分數。<br />\n為免影響比賽公正性及體驗，會員<span style=\"color: red;\">不能再次回覆</span>以<span style=\"color: red;\">修改或增加投票選項</span>，請考慮好心水決定才作回覆投選。</div><br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">附加賽不設額外分數，會員請踴躍投票支持參賽者。</div>"},{"pid":"0acfa8e0a2b39eccceb878f875e2c2a2f6746cbf","tid":251192,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:49:48.000Z","msg":"為方便會員投選,大家可引用以下列表以便發佈投票選項<br />\n<br />\nLIHKG香港乙組女神聯賽升班附加賽四強首回合<br />\n2017-5-21 2pm-7pm<br />\n何雁詩vs周慧敏<br />\n駱文捷vs游蕙禎"},{"pid":"42e00e83cf770b66db9c976e3b96bc96cb85d8f5","tid":251192,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-20T16:50:02.000Z","msg":"其餘升班附加賽賽程請參閱下址<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/248638/page/1</a>"},{"pid":"9db365b8cf8837397f671e99cf2398b0195eef5c","tid":251192,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T03:44:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f907dd1201d35863a9862b235488cbaa2a559314","tid":251192,"uid":56847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:15:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n樓豬代投<br />\n周慧敏同游B"},{"pid":"d526d3aef0d7dade13424a920f92f260645a183d","tid":251192,"uid":269,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:18:35.000Z","msg":"如果兩回合都打和會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"826b28883851e216e003acf81463a00ae6ca3569","tid":251192,"uid":92376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果兩回合都打和會點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有諗過,但係應該唔會發生"},{"pid":"0ca935a787771be0eac12bfbef6b2413d0da2951","tid":251192,"uid":20816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-21T04:36:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如